      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I'm selling my reliable car that's been such a treat to drive. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-maintained, so it's ready for all your upcoming road trips! It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the 'brand new' price tag. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin!",
