    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback this platform is known for. While showing minor signs of road use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a prime candidate for a dedicated driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
