    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. This car has been a dependable daily driver and has been maintained with an open checkbook, as evidenced by a comprehensive binder of service records included with the sale. The exterior finish still holds a brilliant luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a faint scratch near the trunk latch, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary. The premium upholstery is in excellent shape, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every feature, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and panoramic sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, delivering smooth power with no unusual noises or vibrations. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a set of high-performance tires with plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
