      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the professional who demands reliability and sophistication. It features a well-documented service history and remains in a commendable state of preservation, both mechanically and aesthetically. Every component reflects a commitment to quality, ensuring a driving experience that is as composed as it is dependable. This offering represents a prudent acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking a balanced synthesis of value and performance.",
