    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it\u2019s ready to go and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s clean and ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
      "price": 29900.0,
