    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp via six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the critical VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe reinforced for long-term structural integrity. The limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up, while the suspension retains its factory-spec agility with aluminum control arms and firm damping. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system refresh. Though it carries minor cosmetic patina, its performance envelope remains sharp, offering the tactile steering feedback and linear power delivery defining this M-division icon.",
